    dc:creator "Reid, Chris A. M.; De Little, David W." ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Paropsisterna Motschulsky, 1860, a significant pest of plantation eucalypts in Tasmania and Ireland (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Chrysomelinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218073>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218076>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218075> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218073>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Paropsisterna species, live adults. 1, Paropsisterna selmani, new species, post-hibernation, Tasmania (DWdL); 2, Paropsisterna selmani, new species, pre-hibernation, London (Paula French); 3, Paropsisterna selmani, new species, teneral, Ireland (Finbarr Horgan); 4, P. g l o r i o s a (Blackburn, 1899), Gisbourne, Victoria (Eunice Tan)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218073/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218076>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Third instar larva of Paropsisterna selmani, new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218076/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218075>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 13. Paropsisterna species, penis dorsal, apical edge & lateral: 9, P. selmani, new species, Myrtleford, Tasmania; 10, P. g l o r i o s a (Blackburn, 1899), Black Springs, NSW; 11, P. nobilitata (Erichson, 1842), Strahan, Tasmania; 12, P. annularis (Blackburn, 1899), Canberra, ACT; 13, P. debilis (Chapuis, 1877), Nannup, WA. All drawn to same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218075/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

